{"tid":475191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【何志平被捕】眼科權威棄醫從政 2003為港求下籤最「經典」","createTime":"2017-11-21T01:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T02:41:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"00b89521c56cb1efb50831d346d76b1aa40ffc6b","tid":475191,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T01:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171121/large/1511224324_f5f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F1511224324_f5f6.jpg&h=b4aa7fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n何志平2002年7月獲時任特首董建華委任為民政事務局局長，2003年大年初三曾因替香港求得下籤而成為城中話題。<br />\n<br />\n2003年何志平為香港求得下下籤，當年即發生「沙士」事年，導致299人死亡；政府強推「廿三條」立法，觸發50萬人上街；財政司司長梁錦松被指偷步買車，結果與強推廿三條的保安局局長葉劉淑儀雙雙下台。翌年改由劉皇發代表香港求籤。<br />\n<br />\n何志平棄醫從政之前，在1988年成為全港首位眼科全職教授外，更曾任香港眼科醫學會會長，擁有英美等國專業資格，就玻璃體切割手術治療視網膜脫離著書立說，是眼科權威。<br />\n<br />\n何志平1976年在美國田納西州溫德堡大學取得醫學博士名銜，在哈佛任助教後，1980年代返中大執教鞭，1994年起私人執業，踏上行醫之路。<br />\n<br />\n何志平經歷兩段婚姻，與前妻有兩子女，1997年娶台灣女星胡慧中為第二任妻子，育有一女。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171121/57484127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57484127&d=hsX%2F77ntAbKEiH7ho7Lmcozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=118bb691\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F57484127&h=4e5582c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171121/57484127</a>"},{"pid":"2acef4dccf951642ef4565ee59b7396bc931c865","tid":475191,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:22:10.000Z","msg":"何志平係咪射喱眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個樣好弱智  一啲都唔sharp醒"},{"pid":"ea2fb9a5454304aa180400ea3c082eaac28db55e","tid":475191,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:28:26.000Z","msg":"下下籤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1f29e5d86b4c3d8deaf69bd98837d236d04c75","tid":475191,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"有醫生唔做做隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}